    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently maintained to ensure reliability. The engine runs strong and the transmission shifts smoothly, making it a dependable choice for daily commuting or longer trips. While the interior and exterior show some minor signs of normal wear and tear consistent with its age, all major mechanical systems and electronic features are fully functional. Prospective buyers can expect a solid, well-performing car that is ready for the road without needing immediate repairs.",
